EnumCountry.description: The ISO country code for the system, territory, address etc - as appropriate to the context.

EnumCurrencyCode.description: The ISO currency code for currency values as defined by the context e.g. for limits/deductibles or premiums/commissions.

EnumException.description: Exception codes for the process that define a failure or warning.

EnumOrgType.description: The type of party/entity such as a business entity, employee or external person.

EnumResponseStatus.description: A technical status that defines whether a process has been successful or otherwise.

EnumTerritory.description: Territory code decribing main geographical grouping.

EnumMarshGlobalRelationship.description: Marsh Global Relationship tree, e.g. 'Lost Prospect Tree' - Category: MARSH_GLOBAL_RELATIONSHIP.

EnumMarshUsRelationship.description: Marsh US buying status relationship, e.g. 'Prospect' - Category: MARSH_RELATIONSHIP

EnumDnBHierarchyType.description: D&B Hierarchy Type, e.g. 'Single Site' - Category: DNB_HIER_TYP

EnumStatusCode.description: The status of a party/entity e.g. verified, unverified.

EnumPersonStatusCode.description: The person status, e.g. Active, Inactive, Unmanaged - Category: PSN_STAT.

EnumMarketStatusCode.description: Market Status Codes, e.g. 'Merger' - Category: MARKET_STATUS.

EnumMasterCompanyStatusCode.description: Master Company Status Codes, e.g. 'Active', 'Inactive' - Category: CMPY_MSTR_COMPANY_STATUS.

EnumBusinessRoleCd.description: Business Role Codes, e.g. 'Carrier', 'Client' - Category: BL_ROL

EnumCompanySecurityRatingCode.description: Security Rating Code for the company

EnumYesNoFlag.description: Enumeration for flag fields - yes, no, or unknown (U)

EnumClientSegmentCode.description: Identifies the Marsh segment for the company e.g. commercial, risk management, middle market.

EnumLanguageScriptCode.description: ISO15924 Language writing script e.g., Latin, Cyrillic, Han Simplified,  Han Traditional
